archimate:ArchimateDiagramModel.name: SAR SD2.1 Specification of Requirements Realization
archimate:ArchimateDiagramModel.documentation:
This view shows how the security baseline SD2.1 requirements are addressed.
These security baseline requirements stipulate a minimum level of requirements that need to be considered for our solution. Some of these requirements are out scoped because of the nature of our solution.
